name: R2_v2_0396_for_R4B
title: Cross-version VS for R2.v2 Coding System for use in FHIR R4B
description: This cross-version ValueSet represents concepts from http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/v2-0396|2.8.2 for use in FHIR R4B. Concepts not present here have direct `equivalent` mappings crossing all versions from R2 to R4B.
